• Municipal Accountant and the General Services Officer to maintain PPE Ledger Cards and Property Cards for easy reconciliation of the account;
• General Services Officer maintain PAR and ensure its renewal every three years; and
• Municipal Accountant, after reconciliation of PPE records, to effect necessary adjusting entries for variances noted, if any, to establish a more accurate and reliable balance of the PPE.

