Prepare JEV to remove from the Other Supplies and Materials Inventory accounts the semi-expendable properties/items amounting to P31,123,592.05 and reclassify the same to its appropriate expense accounts;
Strictly apply the perpetual inventory method in accounting inventories pursuant to Section 114 of the MNGAS for LGUs;
Write-down the cost of the expired and obsolete office supplies to its NRV. If the NRV is nil, derecognized the same and record the corresponding inventory losses in the books; and
Require the concerned officials of the DCSSJC to provide the CAD and the CGSD copy of pertinent documents as regards the donations and issuances of the ICT tools, devices and gadgets received from the DICT amounting to P62,753,000.00, for their appropriate disposition.

