make systematic and realistic forecasting of revenue taking into account prior years’ experience and statistics as aids in setting attainable targets;
enhance tax collection efficiency by launching a vigorous tax information campaign supported by intensified collection efforts to meet the targets.  For RPT, consider sending out early the notices of assessment to property owners;
